  "usageNotes": "<p>All data files are saved as .mat files, which can be opened with MatLab or python. The software is written in MatLab.</p>\n<p>The analysis software integrates with the following toolboxes:</p>\n<p>Chronux: <a href=\"http://chronux.org/\">http://chronux.org/</a></p>\n<p>FOOOF: <a href=\"https://github.com/fooof-tools/fooof\">https://github.com/fooof-tools/fooof</a> </p>\n<p>Neurostat: <a href=\"https://github.com/iahncajigas/nSTAT\">https://github.com/iahncajigas/nSTAT</a></p>\n<p>PPSSM: <a href=\"https://github.com/josefinacmenendez/PPSSM\">https://github.com/josefinacmenendez/PPSSM</a></p>",
